// After someone submits their first receipt

await whatsapp.sendMessage(phoneNumber, {
  type: 'image',
  image: {
    link: 'https://yourcdn.com/share-qr.png'
  },
  caption: `âœ… You're entered in tonight's R200 draw!

ğŸ’¡ Want bonus entries?
Forward this image to 3 friends.
For every friend who enters, you get +1 bonus entry!

Your referral link: wa.me/27123456789?text=Friend+recommended+me`
});
```

**Why this works:**
- Native WhatsApp behavior (people forward stuff)
- Incentivized (bonus entries)
- Visual (QR code image is self-contained)
- Trackable (unique referral codes)

