- Sandton City mall entrance
- Rosebank Mall
- Eastgate shopping center
- Alexandra taxi rank

Cape Town:
- Cape Town Station
- Century City
- Canal Walk
- Claremont station
- Khayelitsha taxi rank

Durban:
- Workshop Mall
- Gateway Theatre of Shopping
- Durban Station
- Umlazi Mega City

Pretoria:
- Pretoria Station
- Menlyn Park
- Hatfield Plaza
- Mamelodi taxi rank

STRATEGY:
- Target taxi ranks (commuters = daily shoppers)
- Mall parking lots (just shopped = fresh receipts)
- University campuses (students share virally)
- Community centers (trust + reach)
```

**Distribution teams:**
```
OPTION 1: Student Brand Ambassadors
- Hire 2-3 students per city
- R150/day + transport
- 4 hours/day (afternoon rush)
- Target: 200 flyers distributed/day
- Bonus: R5 per verified signup

Cost: R450/day per city
      R13,500/month (3 cities, 5 days/week)

OPTION 2: Community Partnerships
- Partner with local organizations
- They distribute at events
- Revenue share on signups
- Lower cost, higher trust

Cost: R0 upfront
      Revenue share: 10% of prize pool
```

